#MOBILES
#8500
Motoko Kusanagi~
Motoko~
Motoko Kusanagi stands looking at you calmly.
~
Matoko is an expert on unlawful activity, demolitions and secret intelligence. 
She originally worked for a special maneuver team at the Ministry of Home Affairs,
but now works for Section 9, commanding the team with Bateau and Togusa.
~
human~
