stand stand male 3500
0 0 medium 0
#8502
Togusa man~
Togusa~
Togusa sits here, working on an computer.
~
Togusa is the most human part of Section 9. The only thing about him that is 
Cybernetic is a small patch in his brain that allows him to communicate with
the rest of the team.
~
human~
