DFHKT AB FJL 0
sit stand male 3500
0 0 medium 0
#8503
aramaki man~
Aramaki~
Aramaki, head of Section 9, watches the study of the Puppet Master here.
~
Chief Aramaki is both intelligent and resourceful... he has to be to 
control the "unique" personalities of Section 9 (Mainly Kusanagi and 
Bateau). As for how long he has been the chief, no one can remember 
when he wasn't. He is a very straight forward person, and does what 
it takes to get a job done.
~
human~
BG DFH 700 0
110 2 50d100+18000 20d100+500 12d11+10 punch
-70 -70 -70 -70
EFHKT AB FG 0
stand stand male 3500
0 0 medium 0
#8504
ishikawa man~
Ishikawa~
Ishikawa hacks into databases looking for information here.
~
Ishikawa is the oldest mamber of Section 9 next to Aramaki. He is relied 
upon to keep cool in a crisis and help the team to remain focused.
~
human~
