0 0 medium 0
#8505
Puppet Master~
Puppet Master~
Project 2501, or the Puppet Master, is attached to a wall here.
~
"The Puppet Master" is the code name of the program created by the 
Ministry of Foreign Affairs to conduct diplomatic conspiracy activities. 
It has access to all the computer networks in the world and is quite 
powerful. After accessing so many databases, nets, and programs, "The 
Puppet Master" has declared sentience and now seeks political asylum. 
It wishes to exist outside of the net... and to be that which humans 
are: Alive. It wishes to reproduce and die and that is where Kusanagi 
comes in...
~
human~
BGU DFHP 500 0
120 2 50d100+25000 50d100+1000 12d12+0 stab
-80 -80 -80 -80
ACEFHJK AB CD 0
stand stand none 4500
0 0 medium 0
