#8501
The Lobby~
The lobby is plushly decorated. Directly in the middle of the room 
is a circular couch spread out around a wooden coffee table. To the 
west is an elevator to the underground parking lot. To the east is 
an elevator to the minimum security wing of Section 9 HQ. To the 
north is an elevator to the High Security wing of Section 9 HQ.
~
